snippet.title: Elizabeth Holmes testifies in trial she tried to kill the Wall Street Journal Theranos story
snippet.description:
During her trial, Elizabeth Holmes denied hiring a research firm to look into a Wall Street Journal reporter but admitted she tried to kill his Theranos story. Jamie Yuccas spoke with a Wall Street Journal reporter who covered the trial from the beginning.

Each weekday morning, "CBS Mornings” co-hosts Gayle King, Tony Dokoupil and Nate Burleson bring you the latest breaking news, smart conversation and in-depth feature reporting. "CBS Mornings" airs weekdays at 7 a.m. on CBS and 8 a.m. ET on CBSN.
